 {
  "text": "Hello, Anna. This is a quick message before our video call. Please open the link in your email. Turn on your camera and your microphone. If you can't hear me, check the connection. If there is noise, use the mute button. I can see your screen now. See you on the call.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a19_listening1.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Today I had a video call with the team in Sao Paulo. First, I opened the link and I did the login. Then I turned on my camera and my microphone. At the start, I could not hear well, so I checked the connection. After that, I shared my screen with the report. The call was clear and easy. I can do a video call in English now.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a19_listening2.mp3"
 },
 {
